name: MapObject
description: MapObject represents a map object created in the editor or spawned at runtime using Map static methods.

instanceFields.label: Static
instanceFields.description: Object does not move

instanceFields.label: Position
instanceFields.description: The position of the object

instanceFields.label: LocalPosition
instanceFields.description: The local position of the object

instanceFields.label: Rotation
instanceFields.description: The rotation of the object

instanceFields.label: LocalRotation
instanceFields.description: The local rotation of the object

instanceFields.label: QuaternionRotation
instanceFields.description: The rotation of the object as a quaternion

instanceFields.label: QuaternionLocalRotation
instanceFields.description: The local rotation of the object as a quaternion

instanceFields.label: Forward
instanceFields.description: The forward direction of the object

instanceFields.label: Up
instanceFields.description: The up direction of the object

instanceFields.label: Right
instanceFields.description: The right direction of the object

instanceFields.label: Scale
instanceFields.description: The scale of the object

instanceFields.label: Name
instanceFields.description: The name of the object

instanceFields.label: Parent
instanceFields.description: The parent of the object

instanceFields.label: Active
instanceFields.description: Whether the object is active

instanceFields.label: Transform
instanceFields.description: The transform of the object

instanceFields.label: HasRenderer
instanceFields.description: Whether the object has a renderer

instanceFields.label: Color
instanceFields.description: The color of the object

instanceFields.label: TextureTilingX
instanceFields.description: The x tiling of the object's texture

instanceFields.label: TextureTilingY
instanceFields.description: The y tiling of the object's texture

instanceFields.label: TextureOffsetX
instanceFields.description: The x offset of the object's texture

instanceFields.label: TextureOffsetY
instanceFields.description: The y offset of the object's texture

instanceFields.label: ID
instanceFields.description: The ID of the object

instanceFields.label: Tag
instanceFields.description: The tag of the object

instanceFields.label: Layer
instanceFields.description: The layer of the object

instanceFields.label: Rigidbody
instanceFields.description: The Rigidbody component of the MapObject, is null if not added.

instanceFields.label: NetworkView
instanceFields.description: The NetworkView attached to the MapObject, is null if not initialized yet.

instanceMethods.label: AddComponent
instanceMethods.description: Add a component to the object

parameters.name: name
parameters.description: The name of the component to add.

instanceMethods.label: RemoveComponent
instanceMethods.description: Remove a component from the object

parameters.name: name
parameters.description: The name of the component to remove.

instanceMethods.label: GetComponent
instanceMethods.description: Get a component from the object

parameters.name: name
parameters.description: The name of the component to get.

instanceMethods.label: SetComponentEnabled
instanceMethods.description: Set whether a component is enabled

parameters.name: name
parameters.description: The name of the component.

parameters.name: enabled
parameters.description: Whether the component should be enabled.

instanceMethods.label: SetComponentsEnabled
instanceMethods.description: Set whether all components are enabled

parameters.name: enabled
parameters.description: Whether all components should be enabled.

instanceMethods.label: AddSphereCollider
instanceMethods.description: Add a sphere collider to the object

parameters.name: collideMode
parameters.description: The collision mode (e.g., "Region", "Hitboxes").

parameters.name: collideWith
parameters.description: What the collider should collide with (e.g., "Hitboxes").

parameters.name: center
parameters.description: The center position of the sphere collider.

parameters.name: radius
parameters.description: The radius of the sphere collider.

instanceMethods.label: AddBoxCollider
instanceMethods.description: Add a box collider to the object

parameters.name: collideMode
parameters.description: The collision mode (e.g., "Region", "Hitboxes").

parameters.name: collideWith
parameters.description: What the collider should collide with (e.g., "Hitboxes").

parameters.name: center
parameters.description: The center position of the box collider (optional, defaults to calculated bounds).

parameters.name: size
parameters.description: The size of the box collider (optional, defaults to calculated bounds).

instanceMethods.label: AddSphereTarget
instanceMethods.description: Add a sphere target to the object

parameters.name: team
parameters.description: The team that can target this (e.g., "Human", "Titan").

parameters.name: center
parameters.description: The center position of the sphere target.

parameters.name: radius
parameters.description: The radius of the sphere target.

instanceMethods.label: AddBoxTarget
instanceMethods.description: Add a box target to the object

parameters.name: team
parameters.description: The team that can target this (e.g., "Human", "Titan").

parameters.name: center
parameters.description: The center position of the box target.

parameters.name: size
parameters.description: The size of the box target.

instanceMethods.label: GetChild
instanceMethods.description: Get a child object by name

parameters.name: name
parameters.description: The name of the child object to get.

instanceMethods.label: GetChildren
instanceMethods.description: Get all child objects.

instanceMethods.label: GetTransform
instanceMethods.description: Get a child transform by name

parameters.name: name
parameters.description: The name of the transform to get.

instanceMethods.label: SetColorAll
instanceMethods.description: Set the color of all renderers on the object

parameters.name: color
parameters.description: The color to set.

instanceMethods.label: InBounds
instanceMethods.description: Check if a position is within the object's bounds

parameters.name: position
parameters.description: The position to check.

instanceMethods.label: GetBoundsAverageCenter
instanceMethods.description: Get the bounds average center.

instanceMethods.label: GetBoundsCenter
instanceMethods.description: Get the bounds center.

instanceMethods.label: GetBoundsSize
instanceMethods.description: Get the bounds size.

instanceMethods.label: GetBoundsMin
instanceMethods.description: Get the bounds min.

instanceMethods.label: GetBoundsMax
instanceMethods.description: Get the bounds max.

instanceMethods.label: GetBoundsExtents
instanceMethods.description: Get the bounds extents.

instanceMethods.label: GetCorners
instanceMethods.description: Get the corners of the bounds.

instanceMethods.label: HasTag
instanceMethods.description: Whether or not the object has the given tag

parameters.name: tag
parameters.description: The tag to check for.

instanceMethods.label: AddBuiltinComponent
instanceMethods.description: Add a builtin component to the MapObject

parameters.name: name
parameters.description: The name of the builtin component to add (e.g., "DayLight").

instanceMethods.label: GetBuiltinComponent
instanceMethods.description: Gets a builtin component to the MapObject

parameters.name: name
parameters.description: The name of the builtin component to get.

instanceMethods.label: RemoveBuiltinComponent
instanceMethods.description: Remove a builtin component from the MapObject

parameters.name: name
parameters.description: The name of the builtin component to remove.

instanceMethods.label: ConvertToCSV
instanceMethods.description: Serialize the current object to a csv.
